  PreLevelDialogue:
  - "Hey NICE job on those shapes kid! Is it just me or can you already SMELL the
    money. It smells good doesn\u2019t it?"
  - "Woah woah hold your horses, I still don\u2019t trust you fully to not MESS IT
    UP for both of us."
  - "No no, it\u2019s not like that. You\u2019re not that bad! I mean WOW the state
    of that simple geometry! Heh, okay okay, Bill\u2019s got some more marble for
    you, and I\u2019ve got some more complicated targets for you to cut."
  - "But before you start cutting through the whole block with your sword again,
    like a MANIAC, I\u2019ve got a present for you. A \u2018Tanto\u2019."
  - "(Bill I love you you\u2019re so cool) WOAH no need to get so excited it\u2019s
    just what I do!"
  - "Anyway, you\u2019re probably wondering why I gave this to you, well with this
    fancy new tool, you should be able to control your cutting more. You will be
    able to cut a specific amount of the way through the marble."
  - "Think of all of the new shapes you can cut! Well fortunately for you you don\u2019t
    need to think of it because you WILL be doing it."
  - Now as a matter of fact. Come on, get to it!
